Flow.description: Email notification will be sent when Case Status is set to “Awaiting Invoice”, the Record Type is “Managed Care” AND 5 days have passed.

value.stringValue:
'Hello –

This is the 3rd follow-up in reference to '+ [Case].Subject_for_Managed_Care_Notifications__c +'. Our records indicate that this service call has been completed on '+TEXT((DATEVALUE([Case].Job_Completion_Date__c))) +', however we have not received your invoice. Please take one of the following actions:

Reply directly to this email with your invoice attached.
Email your invoice to the following:nainvoice.champion@gardnerdenver.com
Fax your invoice to: 217-221-8747

Your rates with Champion Managed Care:
Labor: '+TEXT([Case].Service_Center_Labor__c) +'
Travel: '+TEXT([Case].Service_Center_Travel__c)+ '

Thank you and have a great day!
' +[Case].Owner:User.FirstName + ' '+[Case].Owner:User.LastName + '
Champion Managed Care'
